data.description: This house is a stunning property that boasts three bedrooms and one full bathroom, all new windows and multiple areas freshly painted along with a large backyard and an upgraded workshop or detached garage. The open floor plan creates a spacious and welcoming environment, perfect for hosting guests as the custom fish tank give a conversional piece. The windows in the dining area provides a beautiful view of the backyard and fills the room with natural light. The recessed lighting throughout the house adds a modern touch and creates a warm and inviting atmosphere. The wet bar is perfect for a quick refreshment or entertaining guests in the living area. The large yard has mature trees, providing ample shade. The metal roof, front pergola, fresh landscaping, and covered back patio is perfect for hosting outdoor gatherings and enjoying the beautiful Texas weather. This beautiful property with all the amenities is incredibly inviting. It's perfect for anyone looking for a comfortable and elegant home to call their own in Poth ISD.
